	<p>
		Flip.TV is provided to you as a free service in the hope that you find
		our TV search and alert service useful and convenient.  Although we 
		receive some income from the associated advertisements, ad revenues currently
		don't cover our daily costs to maintain our servers on the web. We are
		also trying to enhance the service with new features for our users.
	</p>
	<p>
